The position of '''Prime Minister''' was the political leader of [[Bakura/Legends|Bakura]].

Prime Minister also was the leading member of the [[Bakuran Senate]], though not counted as a senator. During the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] occupation of Bakura, the position of Prime Minister seems to have become merely the head of government, with the Imperial [[Governor/Legends|governor]] being head of state (although holding de facto supreme power).

